			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) Start new game\r\n2) Go to Wyrm's Crossing Smithy. (-2.328; 49.031; -49.241)\r\n3) Encounter OrinSmith and she'll eventually teleport away.\r\n4) RealSmith should awaken and confront the player.\r\n5) Talk to him and succeed the skill check to de-escalate the situation with him.\r\n6) Long-Rest.\r\n7) He should have disappeared and a puddle of blood is where he used to be.\r\n8) PAD should occur when you are nearby the bloodpuddle."
				},
				"defaultAttitudes": [
					{}
				],
				"defaultEmotions": [
					{}
				],
				"isImportantForStagings": [
					{}
				],
				"isPeanuts": [
					{}
				],
				"needLayout": {
					"type": 19,
					"value": 0
				},
				"nextNodeId": {
					"type": 5,
					"value": 1
				},
				"speakerSlotDescription": [
					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Orin had impersonated the Smith. And tried to frame the players by impersonating them and attacking the Smith - in the effort to get the players to kill the Smith. If the players had succeeded in de-escalating the situation with the Smith. Orin will return on LongRest (or when players travel to LOW) and kill off the Smith anyways.\r\n\r\nThis PAD is triggered when players are near the bloodstain marks of where the Smith usually is. His body can later be found in Bhaal Temple."
				}
			}
		}
